title: Jets rookie, USC alum Williams shows support for Trojans
text: Jets rookie, USC alum Williams shows support for Trojans Thursday, 15 October 2015 (5 minutes ago) New York Jets rookie defensive lineman Leonard Williams wore a white USC Trojans T-shirt in the locker room Wednesday in support of the football program, which was rocked Monday when coach Steve Sarkisian was fired
